      <scopecontent id="aspace_61a1720c4dd422c4158401728bb0e5fd">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of posters, leaflets, and other materials distributed by various Russian parties and movements supporting and opposing Boris Yeltsin and his policies. On 25 April 1993, Russia held a referendum on support for President Boris Yeltsin and his policies. The referendum included two non-binding questions concerning Yeltsin and his socio- economic policies, and two questions concerning pre-term elections for the presidency and People's Deputies of the Russian Federation. The results showed high support for Yeltsin and his policies but did not require early elections.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
